@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy - Hospital Management System";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <!-- Page Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
            <p>Your privacy is our priority. Below is the policy governing the collection, use, and protection of your personal and health information.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Privacy Policy Content -->
        <div class="privacy-policy">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>We collect the following types of information when you use our healthcare services:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Personal Information:</strong> Name, date of birth, contact information, insurance details.</li>
                        <li><strong>Health Information:</strong> Medical history, diagnoses, treatment plans, prescriptions, and test results.</li>
                        <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent on the site, IP address, and cookies.</li>
                        <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> Credit card details, billing information, and payment history for medical services rendered.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mt-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Your information is used for the following purposes:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Providing healthcare services, consultations, and treatments.</li>
                        <li>Billing and payment processing for medical services.</li>
                        <li>Personalizing your experience and improving our services.</li>
                        <li>Sending appointment reminders and health-related notifications.</li>
                        <li>Complying with healthcare regulations and legal requirements.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mt-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>3. How We Protect Your Data</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>We implement the highest standards of data security to protect your personal and health information:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Encryption of sensitive health data both in transit and at rest.</li>
                        <li>Access controls to limit who can view or edit your information.</li>
                        <li>Regular security audits to detect vulnerabilities.</li>
                        <li>Compliance with healthcare privacy regulations (e.g., HIPAA, GDPR).</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mt-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>4. Your Rights</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>You have the following rights regarding your personal and health information:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Right to access your health records and personal information.</li>
                        <li>Right to request corrections to your medical information if it is inaccurate.</li>
                        <li>Right to request deletion of your information, in accordance with applicable laws.</li>
                        <li>Right to opt-out of non-essential communications (e.g., marketing).</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mt-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>5. Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>We use cookies and other tracking technologies to improve your experience on our website:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Cookies to remember your preferences and settings.</li>
                        <li>Analytics cookies to monitor site usage and improve functionality.</li>
                        <li>You may disable cookies in your browser, but it may impact website functionality.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="card mt-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>6. Sharing of Information</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>Your information may be shared under the following circumstances:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>With healthcare providers involved in your care (e.g., specialists, labs, hospitals).</li>
                        <li>With third-party service providers for payment processing, IT support, and analytics.</li>
                        <li>When required by law or to comply with government regulations (e.g., reporting to health authorities).</li>
                        <li>For emergency situations where your health or safety is at risk.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Changes to Privacy Policy -->
            <div class="card mt-4">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Any changes will be posted here, and the date of the latest update will be indicated at the top of this page.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="text-center mt-5">
            <p>. All rights reserved. | <a href="/terms">Terms & Conditions</a></p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JavaScript -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
